title: The Green Hornet Strikes Again!
actors: Warren Hull, Wade Boteler, Anne Nagel, Keye Luke, Eddie Acuff, Pierre Watkin, James Seay, Arthur Loft, Joe Devlin, William Hall, Dorothy Lovett, Jay Michael, Charles Miller, Jean Brooks, Irving Mitchell
description: A wealthy publisher uses a disguise and calls himself the Green Hornet to fight crime in his city.
